name: MiniKeePassX
body:
### Welcome.

MiniKeePassX is a brand new password tool for Mac OS X. While it is based on the KeePass library implemented in the [MiniKeePass](http://minikeepass.github.com) iOS App, the application is inspired by the reference implementation [KeePass Password Save](http://keepass.info) and [KeePassX](http://www.keepassx.org). MiniKeePassX can load and save files created with KeePass Password Save, MiniKeePass or KeePassX.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
